[[ja:小錦中]] * Tenmu's reign (684). * {{ill|Kose no Kurohito|ja|巨勢黒麻呂}} - Middle counselor (chūnagon).
== References == {{reflist}}
== See Also == * {{ill|Rank and position changes in Japan|ja|冠位・位階制度の変遷}}
